<aside class="bike-form-details">
  <h2 class="bike-form-details">Details</h2>
  <div class="form-group">
  <select class="form-control" placeholder="Make">
    <option selected disabled>Make</option>
    <option>1</option>
    <option>2</option>
    <option>3</option>
    <option>4</option>
  </select>

  <select class="form-control" placeholder="Model">
    <option selected disabled>Model</option>
    <option>1</option>
    <option>2</option>
    <option>3</option>
    <option>4</option>
  </select>

  <select class="form-control" placeholder="Year">
    <option selected disabled>Year</option>
    <option>1</option>
    <option>2</option>
    <option>3</option>
    <option>4</option>
  </select>
</div>
</aside>

<main class="bike-form-details">
  <h2 class="bike-form-description">Description</h2>
  <p>Tell renters why your bike is cool. Do you have an amazing frame?
    Is your bike perfect for touring? Will it travel through time if it hits
    30 MPH? This is your chance to share why you love your bike.</p>
  <textarea class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>

  <h2 class="bike-form-description">Location</h2>

  <div class="bike-form-location-inputs">
    <div class="address">
      <label for="street-address" id="autocomplete" class="bike-form-location">Street Address</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control address" value="" id="street-address">
    </div>

    <div class="zip">
      <label for="zip" class="bike-form-location">zip</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control zip" value="" id="zip">
    </div>
  </div>
  <p> Provide an exact address where renters can pick up your bike.</p>
  <div class="map bike-form"></div>
  <input type="submit" value="Save bike" class="btn save-bike-button">
</main>
